{"tid":2295302,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影邊個角色最慘？","createTime":"2020-11-21T16:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T10:25:23.000Z","uid":41414,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"8b19dba1888cd7bc97b5c6147415639006584e8e","tid":2295302,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"李洛克 好有毅力 細細個靠努力做到忍者<br />\n<br />\n然而火影話你聽努力係冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n比我愛羅屌打 <br />\n<br />\n後期大戰又係冇咩用<br />\n<br />\n戰略價值又細 唔似豬鹿蝶<br />\n<br />\n豬成個戰場溝通用佢 完美輔助<br />\n<br />\n鹿盟軍大腦之一<br />\n<br />\n蝶就開無雙 根本就戰爭機器<br />\n<br />\n白眼戰略價值高 <br />\n<br />\n蟲佬 同赤丸都係aoe <br />\n<br />\n主角三人組唔使講 就連天天都好有用<br />\n<br />\n但係小李就完全冇鏡頭 就係個垃圾<br />\n<br />\n又唔夠佢老師咁勁 真係好撚慘"},{"pid":"f6ebe3c8f64c368a155219cddd978c10888ee9b6","tid":2295302,"uid":191300,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"疾風傳入面的疾風，主角名，瞬間收皮。"},{"pid":"7cb935d4cb2ed99b5050960560bd4911127b8e70","tid":2295302,"uid":8410,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"成套唯一死左嗰個日向， 死咗仲唔係最慘？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df194cfae627e99d1c68d326ae1d73c02f2cab72","tid":2295302,"uid":316697,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"itachi係最慘<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"4f93c34e97567d39f7c038b5b0ca4d05c839ccf5","tid":2295302,"uid":62850,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"天天有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da4f516a0fda444a9257b9d978c04ea88cc937d","tid":2295302,"uid":247085,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"佐助全家都係黑警<br />\n抵佢死全家"},{"pid":"677493287f073c81d2cd718c63ffe6a0031999d0","tid":2295302,"uid":303359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"帶人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class